## Personal Reflection

This module helped me understand the ethical and legal foundation of cybersecurity.
Before learning technical attacks, understanding **why** and **how** ethical hackers operate is essential. I now have a clearer roadmap for upcoming modules focusing on reconnaissance, scanning, and exploitation techniques.

